Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Yang] Salem can't be killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- You all heard her too right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- I--\N- There was so much
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.51,0:01:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you hadn't told us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you think that was okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ruby] Professor...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your plan to defeat Salem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.19,0:02:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.46,0:02:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,(loud smacking)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,(wood breaking)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,(soft crunching)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- No one wanted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave my life to you because you gave me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a place in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was finally doing some good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- But, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Meeting you was the worst luck of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him we're not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:03:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like he's locked himself deep inside my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Our head?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,(grunts) I hate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I want it to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- He just left us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- What are we gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,(growls)\N- Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- We need to get a move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be dark before we know it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and every one of you is spewing negativity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a trail over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Trails usually lead somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Lady, I don't know who you think you are but--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- No buts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that you're upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly I'm still coming to terms with the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,this is humanity's second time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But, if we don't move, we die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll be damned if I've lived this long
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,just to die out here in the cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,(wind whistling)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm just going to be another one of his lives, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're your own person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't lie to him, Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,(wind whistling)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,(engine roaring)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,(engine idling)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,(suspenseful music)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- (laughs) Welcome back, welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I do hope you missed us as much as we missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,where is our Fall Maiden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,(gasps and giggles)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Emerald, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't tell me something happened to her? (laughs)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- I will cut off more than just your tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- (chuckles) Careful, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Cinder isn't here to protect you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Back off, freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, don't misunderstand,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I am in mourning just as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it appears you've failed our queen,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,(laughs maniacally)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- I would like you to explain to me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:07:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,how it is you've failed so spectacularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- The Faunus militia split our forces--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me rephrase the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.17,0:07:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is responsible for your defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- I take full responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,(loud banging)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- But that wouldn't be fair now, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We all know who's truly to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,(wet crackling)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,(Hazel grunts)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,(footsteps tapping)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Emerald.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to tell me whose fault this was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,(Emerald breathing heavily)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Cinder!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We failed because of Cinder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to understand that failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to understand why Cinder
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,must be left to toil in her isolation
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,until she redeems herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- You mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Emerald] She's alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you questioning our divine savior?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,(chuckles nervously)\NOf course not, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:09:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's important not to lose sight of what drives us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Reverence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But the moment you put your desires before my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,(Hazel grunts)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,they will be lost to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,(Hazel gasps)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is simply the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The path to your desires is only found through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we must press on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The sword under Vacuo's academy, Shade--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have more to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,(wet crackling)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Qrow and the children are taking the lamp to Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- (laughs) Not if I can help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- And they're being led,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,by Ozpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Tyrian] So soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- He's the only man with a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of getting through to Ironwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,(loud cracking)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Your Grace, I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(suspenseful music)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,(Salem screaming)\N(glass breaking)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- (sighs) Doesn't look like this is gonna let up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Just wanna get this stupid relic to Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's hope we don't have to walk all the way there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- I thought trails led somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do you have nothing better to do
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,than to harass a defenseless old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Everyone, quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,(metallic squeaking)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Blake] Well, at least one good thing happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Weiss] It looks abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's still better than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come on, I think we could all use some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,(wind whooshing)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,(metallic clanging)
